title: Whats the music?

embed.description: Relive the epic journey of the 2015 World Championship!

body:
Hey, what's up? I love this video, and i really want y start music. 
I think it's a edit of "riot games-final choice" but i can't found it.
Anyone knows the name? Thank you very much.

replies.body:
It kind of seems like a mix of all the songs that were used during the 2015 world finals. I don't have specific names but "Final Choice" was definitely the intro. I think the second track that began at about 2:30 was the song used in the London video.

I hope this helps. :)
Yes, i know. But is like a remix of "final choice" i dont know where to find. Thank you very much for you time!
